TOP:RFC_RAT Register Descriptions

TOP:RFC_RAT:RATCNT

Address Offset 0x0000 0004
Physical Address 0x4004 3004 Instance 0x4004 3004
Description Radio Timer Counter Value
Type RW
Bits Field Name Description Type Reset
31:0 CNT Counter value. This is not writable while radio timer counter is enabled. RW 0x0000 0000

TOP:RFC_RAT:RATCH0VAL

Address Offset 0x0000 0080
Physical Address 0x4004 3080 Instance 0x4004 3080
Description Timer Channel 0 Capture/Compare Register
Type RW
Bits Field Name Description Type Reset
31:0 VAL Capture/compare value. The system CPU can safely read this register, but it is recommended to use the CPE API commands to configure it for compare mode. RW 0x0000 0000
